net.coderazzi.filters.gui.editors
Interface ChoiceFilterEditor.IChoice

Enclosing class:
ChoiceFilterEditor
public static interface ChoiceFilterEditor.IChoice

Interface to delegate to the application how a selected option in the editor matches a RowFilter.Entry instance.

By default, the ChoiceFilterEditor displays a set of objects that will be matched against the contents of the RowFilter.Entry; by using this interface, the application can decide how the matching is performed.

Note that the list renderer -if any- must know how to display the IChoice objects. The the default Renderer will display them as the string returned by their toString method
